I am really happy to share with you guys that my husband and I are expecting in the fall! We are so grateful and excited. 

My husbands been using our future baby room as an office (WFH) but I’m kicking him out soon and I can’t wait to share some glimpses on stories! 
- Teri #sfbTERI 😊❤️
